## ⚡ Quick Example Walkthrough

nums = [0,1,2,2,3,0,4,2], val = 2

```
i=0 → 0 → keep → nums[0]=0 → k=1  
i=1 → 1 → keep → nums[1]=1 → k=2  
i=2 → 2 → skip  
i=3 → 2 → skip  
i=4 → 3 → keep → nums[2]=3 → k=3  
i=5 → 0 → keep → nums[3]=0 → k=4  
i=6 → 4 → keep → nums[4]=4 → k=5  
i=7 → 2 → skip  
```

👉 Final: first 5 elements valid

